{
  "title": "roasted nutty portuguese peas stir-fry",
  "description": "a quick and flavorful weeknight dish featuring sugar snap peas, garlic, and lemon, all roasted to perfection in a mortar and pestle. this dish is low in sodium and rich in protein and fiber.",
