  "instructions": [
    "preheat the oven to 425°f.",
    "in a mortar and pestle, pound the garlic cloves until well-crushed.",
    "add the lemon juice and pound until well-combined.",
    "in a large bowl, toss the sugar snap peas with the lemon-garlic mixture, olive oil, salt, and pepper until they are evenly coated.",
    "heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the sugar snap peas and cook for 3 minutes.",
    "transfer the skillet to the preheated oven and roast for 10 minutes.",
    "remove the skillet from the oven and stir in the chopped parsley and grated lemon zest.",
    "serves hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
  ],
